SIMPLE: listless
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Listless
<hw>List"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>listles</ets>,
<ets>lustles</ets>. See <er>Lust</er>.]</ety> <def>Having no desire or
inclination; indifferent; heedless; spiritless.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧ A
<xex>listless</xex> unconcern.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Thomson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Benumbed with cold, and <qex>listless</qex> of their gain.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I was <qex>listless</qex>, and desponding.</q>
<rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Heedless; careless; indifferent; vacant;
uninterested; languid; spiritless; supine; indolent.</syn></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>List"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>List"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lit</ent>⟦br⟧
